---
source: crates/data_components/tests/http_provider_test.rs
description: HTTP provider - glob pattern with double wildcard
---
+---------------+------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| plan_type     | plan                                                                                                                         |
+---------------+------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| logical_plan  | Projection: api.content                                                                                                      |
|               |   Filter: api.request_path = Utf8("/api/v1/users/123")                                                                       |
|               |     TableScan: api projection=[request_path, content], partial_filters=[api.request_path = Utf8("/api/v1/users/123")]        |
| physical_plan | CoalesceBatchesExec: target_batch_size=8192                                                                                  |
|               |   FilterExec: request_path@0 = /api/v1/users/123, projection=[content@1]                                                     |
|               |     RepartitionExec: partitioning=RoundRobinBatch(16), input_partitions=1                                                    |
|               |       CooperativeExec                                                                                                        |
|               |         HttpExec: base_url=https://api.example.com/, format=json, partitions=[(path="/api/v1/users/123", query="", body="")] |
|               |                                                                                                                              |
+---------------+------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
